{"tid":731312,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【山寨貢茶】被踢爆之後火速換招牌　一夜間變「喜茶」山寨版","createTime":"2018-07-06T05:38:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-07T12:50:11.000Z","uid":17646,"like":403,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":96,"replies":[{"pid":"0ff1af53296ef6353a8b4bbeab3e4746389ad30a","tid":731312,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T05:38:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1616858/org/662efa2accda301262113eb6e0ada126.jpg/d35iYh6kx-Ip2mPgSgDCWhr58MERZG2SyPOLX8jzi18?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1616858%2Forg%2F662efa2accda301262113eb6e0ada126.jpg%2Fd35iYh6kx-Ip2mPgSgDCWhr58MERZG2SyPOLX8jzi18%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=013de46a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n昨日《香港01》踢爆太子界限街的台式茶飲店「貢茶」有山寨之嫌，事件引起市民熱話，疑似店主被追訪時更即時落閘狂奔。事隔一晚，該店門面原本寫上「貢茶」的招牌，今日竟已火速更換，變成了「元品」，不過細看之下，商標（LOGO）竟然變成了山寨版的喜茶。<br />\n記者今日中午再到該店現場了解，該店在中午十二時許仍未開舖，不過店頂原本寫上「貢茶」的招牌，已被貼上另一張招牌「元品茶」。<br />\n<br />\n這張「元品茶」的招牌紙，在細看之外，仍然見到「貢茶」字樣在底下。不過，更令人發笑的是，有眼利市民一看這個「元品茶」的商標，竟然與另一內地茶飲品牌「喜茶」有幾分相似。根據「喜茶」網站的商標，是一個卡通男孩子圖像，而「元品茶」則變成了女孩子的卡通圖像。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1616620/org/fe7e4bcc877594c126c498d6edf5cc4c.jpg/7xJ68UxrXJA3Pf2OoRj7viLrTvTOAZGqsgpHtLIKR7Q?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1616620%2Forg%2Ffe7e4bcc877594c126c498d6edf5cc4c.jpg%2F7xJ68UxrXJA3Pf2OoRj7viLrTvTOAZGqsgpHtLIKR7Q%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=eadecda0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1616622/org/8dc76f5eb3ecdf34289176411817f151.jpeg/WppQ-YpkWsRtxhfTBImiYd3QaCgjACwZxhmfUcYZn1E?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1616622%2Forg%2F8dc76f5eb3ecdf34289176411817f151.jpeg%2FWppQ-YpkWsRtxhfTBImiYd3QaCgjACwZxhmfUcYZn1E%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=7fca0bc7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c37babb24549dee433ca20fdba069855ae86fdab","tid":731312,"uid":27432,"like":645,"dis